\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces Ungoverned agent execution (left) versus AgenticContract-governed execution (right). Without governance, every action proceeds unchecked, leading to data loss, budget overruns, and untested deployments. With AgenticContract, every action passes through the policy engine in under 50\,ns, enabling real-time deny, approval gating, and budget enforcement with a complete audit trail.}}{2}{figure.caption.2}\protected@file@percent }
